-- Muralitharan Takes Record 800th Wicket in Final Cricket Test for Sri Lanka
-- Anusha Ondaatjie
-- 2010-07-22T08:25:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/muralitharan-takes-record-800th-wicket-in-his-final-sri-lanka-cricket-test.html

          
          
             Sri Lanka spinner Muttiah
Muralitharan became the first cricketer to take 800 test
wickets, extending his record tally in his final match before
quitting the elite format of the game.  
